      <h3 style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 28px;">Tier 1: Partner Now (500 to 5K followers)</h3>

